    <title>my_first_blog</title>
    <url>/2022/06/18/my-first-blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>这是我的第一个博客测试,</p>
<h1 id="测试数学公式">测试数学公式</h1>
<p><span class="math display">\[
f(x) = x^2
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
g(x)=
\left\{
\begin{align}
&amp; 1, x&lt;1\\
&amp; x, otherwise
\end{align}
\right.
\]</span></p>
]]></content>
