  <entry>
    <title>my_second_blog</title>
    <url>/2022/06/18/my-second-blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="博客测试">博客测试</h1>
<h2 id="图床测试">图床测试</h2>
<p><img data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fenglielie/notes_image/main/img/%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8E%8B%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB.png" /></p>
<h2 id="代码测试">代码测试</h2>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello,world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="公式测试">公式测试</h2>
<ul>
<li>列表项一</li>
<li>列表项二</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\begin{aligned}
\frac{\partial \mathbf{u}}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{u}\cdot \nabla)
\mathbf{u} &amp;= -\nabla p + \nu \nabla^2 \mathbf{u}\\
\nabla \cdot \mathbf{u} &amp;= 0\\
\mathbf{u}|_{\partial \Omega} &amp;= \mathbf{u}_b\\
\mathbf{u}|_{t=0} &amp;= \mathbf{u}_0
\end{aligned}
\]</span></p>
<p>分式 <span class="math display">\[x+1\over\sqrt{1-x^2}
\tag{i}\label{eq_tag}\]</span></p>
<p>行内公式<span class="math inline">\(\frac12\)</span></p>
]]></content>
